* {{ill|Susanoo Shrine (Shibata)|ja|須佐之男神社 (新発田市)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (Tenno Shrine) - Niigata Prefecture, Shibata, {{ill|Tenno (Shibata)|ja|天王 (新発田市)|qq=draft|qq=draft}}<ref>[http://www.niigata-kankou.or.jp/sys/data?page-id=10163], [http://www.niigata-u.com/files/ngt2009g/091010b1.html], [http://shibata-info.jp/archives/eventcal/%E5%A4%A9%E7%8E%8B%E3%81%BE%E3%81%A4%E3%82%8A]</ref>
